data.description: Beautiful detached raised ranch in the Clason Point neighborhood.  Feautures 3 bedrooms, 2 baths, large living room, renovated kitchen, dining area and Foyer over a full walkout finished basement. Oak hardwood floors, new siding, new windows two chimneys and updated bathrooms on a Oversize lot with plenty of parking or entertainment area complete this home. Close to public transportation, shopping, schools, parks and the proposed citywide ferry with connection in the Upper east side and Lower Manhattan.
